{"tid":1666200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（撤回係無用）智利示威者縱火 最少八人死亡","createTime":"2019-10-21T01:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T01:57:16.000Z","uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bfad5cf6b0cac901d84498db92ad90df179e9ac0","tid":1666200,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】智利政府撤回地鐵車費加價後未能平息大規模示威，示威者多處縱火，最少八人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n示威者在首都聖地亞哥街頭繼續與軍方對峙，有人被捕時被士兵強行拖行，軍方繼續在聖地亞哥實施宵禁，更提早至晚上七時就開始。<br />\n<br />\n智利人不滿政府調高繁忙時段地鐵車費，即使政府已經撤回加價決定，但民眾仍然上街，又到處縱火宣洩不滿。<br />\n<br />\n聖地亞哥南部有兩間超市被破壞及搶掠，最少三人被燒死。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司報道，另外五人在一間成衣廠大火中身亡，亦有兩人在警方拘捕行動中槍受傷，全國有超過一千四百人被捕。"},{"pid":"5ebb5d0c1618d03581dac60c517f0f5a4f591d48","tid":1666200,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"加完一成電費，又加地鐵票價，有示威撤回票價就想當無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係天下烏鴉一樣黑"},{"pid":"2373b2245db6e08256a747882846ba755258e697","tid":1666200,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"係咪因為反黑警  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeb90540728116fa1d0d7679c0baf3fa0d45de1","tid":1666200,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2373b2245db6e08256a747882846ba755258e697","tid":1666200,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"係咪因為反黑警  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:32:02.000Z","msg":"可能反埋制度暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9c31948fdc6f0a66eccd003754102da34ff9c4","tid":1666200,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac00a47d61209c6e87e8